Androka, C. 10 km. W. of Ambalavao. Exposed metamorphic rock with succulent Senecio spp., Aloe sp., Xerophyta, Dombeya etc.; caped with remnant dwarf forest of Bauhinia, Allophyllus etc. but much exploited and with naturalised Melia, Psidium & Canna.
